# Ottoman–Maltese wars

There have been several Ottoman–Maltese wars:
* Conquest of Tunis (1535)
* Battle of Preveza
* Algiers expedition (1541)
* Invasion of Gozo (1551)
* Siege of Tripoli (1551)
* Battle of Djerba
* Great Siege of Malta
* Battle of Lepanto
* Raid on Żejtun
* War of Candia
* Morean War
* War of Corfu
